data.description: Blast From the Past- This Early American home boasts large living spaces and bedrooms to make for a comfortable home. There are two separate dining spaces, one of which is connected to the large living area, three nice bedrooms, incredible covered patio, storage building and a nice two car garage closse to the Elementary School. All the open space yields an inviting and large home draw that few homes have.
